    <h1>Strawberry shake</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the simplest recipe for a strawberry shake. You can easily do it at home in a few minutes and enjoy a cold beverage on a sunny day.</p>
    <img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/high-angle-strawberry-milkshake-with-straw-cloth_23-2148707798.jpg?t=st=1744571822~exp=1744575422~hmac=cf6c2ce001ee4dc186eae9df57177bd7182d9f4be7ba1bffd67ed3332e20506b&w=740" alt="Photo of strawberry shake in a glass">
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>2 cups milk</li>
      <li>1 cup frozen strawberries</li>
      <li>1 tablespoon honey</li>
      <li>1 teaspoon vanilla extract</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Pour milk into the cup</li>
      <li>Add strawberries, honey, vanilia</li>
      <li>Blend until consistency is smooth</li>
      <li>Pour into a glass and enjoy</li>
    </ol>
